Package: secretsanta
Title: Generate a Secret Santa list and e-mail the participants!
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Adam",
           family = "Austin",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "ataustin@gmail.com")
Description: secretsanta automates the process of assigning gift givers to
             gift recipients.  The process can be blind to all participants,
             including the organizer who runs the code.  A log file
             will be written to record assignments.
License: `use_mit_license()`
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.1.1
Imports: 
    jsonlite,
    gmailr
